===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm}}, from {{etyl|xno}} {{term|lavendre||lang=fro}} (French: ''[[lavande]]''), from {{etyl|ML.}} {{term|lavendula|lang=la}}, possibly from {{etyl|la}} {{term|lividus||lang=la|bluish}}, but influenced by {{term|lavo|lavare|lang=la|wash}} due to use of lavender in washing clothes.

